Setup 과정

1) Windows 환경
  a. Input method
OK ==> Yes ==> ibus check ==> OK

  b. Language Support
install / remove language ==> Korean

  확인 사항
  Keyboard input method system이 iBus인지 확인

2) Terminal 환경
Ctrl + Alt + T
ibus-setup
Input Method ==> Add ==> … ==> Korean ==> Hangul ==> Add

3) Windows 환경
Setting ==> Region & Language
Input source ==> + ==> Korean(Hangul)
